data.description: Fantastic two-story ALL BRICK home in Northwood close to shopping, restaurants & expressways! Big ticket UPDATES INCLUDE FLAT ROOF (2023); WINDOWS & FURNACE (2016); CENTRAL AIR (2022); HOT WATER TANK (2021). Spacious living room w/coved ceilings & luxury vinyl plank flooring leads into the dining room & kitchen. Convenient main floor mudroom/laundry & half bath. First floor bedroom w/walk-in closet. Second floor offers two bedrooms & a full bath. Large breezeway great for storage leads to 2.5 car garage w/additional storage loft. Private fenced-in back yard w/patio and plenty of green space!
